Speaker 1: I submitted a case about suspending or cancelling my subscription prescriptions and they said

Speaker 1: All right, give me one moment, let me look at your account.

Speaker 2: All right, and your name is Steven, correct?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 1: What seems to be the issue?

Speaker 2: Are you just getting your refills too fast?

Speaker 1: You can choose when you get them, you don't have to get them that fast or monthly or whenever

Speaker 2: you're not ready.

Speaker 1: Yeah, yeah, I was trying to do that online, I just couldn't figure out how to do that.

Speaker 2: We can make that adjustment for you, give me a moment.

Speaker 1: All right, yeah, so basically how that works, sir, so basically in the next five months

Speaker 2: here we won't bill or ship you anything, you're going to have to call us to receive your next

Speaker 1: orders, okay?

Speaker 2: That's fine.

Speaker 1: All right, that's what we're going to do for you.

Speaker 2: Awesome, I hope that works better.

Speaker 1: All right, Ian, well you are all set, sir, we just finished up.

Speaker 2: Have a good one, thanks.

Speaker 1: You too.
